    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed at MRL 5 have achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification confirms that 95th-percentile hemolysis predictions remain below the absolute clinical threshold across all five VAD operating points. Grid convergence, code verification, and independent use-error review provide high confidence in numerical accuracy. Validation against FDA generic pump experimental data at directly relevant conditions demonstrates model predictive capability for absolute hemolysis index. No credibility gaps remain; the package supports acceptance of the CFD model for the Class III VAD hemolysis prediction COU.",
